title: FULL SHOW: We Talk Soulja Boy, Sit Down With Kenya Barris, Ask Yee and More
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: We Talk Soulja Boy, Sit Down With Kenya Barris, Ask Yee and More
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we talk the latest in the alleged altercation between Teddy Riley and Soulja Boy as Soulja was accused of putting hands on Nia Riley while pregnant. Later on we got Kenya Barris in studio to talk "Entergalatic" and More! Yee takes listeners calls and gives relationship and business advice during Ask Yee
